### Health Check
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/

### Get All Commands
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/api/commands?page=1&limit=5

### Get Command by Trigger (using query parameter)
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/api/commands?trigger=%2Fhi1

### Get Command by ID 
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/api/commands/681e68820ce3d72ad1ab36ed


### Create Command
POST http://localhost:{PORT}/api/commands
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Greeting",
    "command": "/hello",
    "text": "Hello there!" 
}



### Update Command
PATCH http://localhost:{PORT}/api/commands/681e6a990ce3d72ad1ab36f8
Content-Type: application/json

{
   "name": "driver-updated"
}

### Delete Command
DELETE http://localhost:{PORT}/api/commands/67fe9cb7e071a32a40d2076e


### V2 Auth - Register User
POST http://localhost:{PORT}/api/v2/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123",
  "username": "testuser"
}

### V2 Auth - Login
POST http://localhost:3015/api/v2/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "davidesparzac59@gmail.com",
  "password": "NewSecurePassword123!"
}

### V2 Commands - Create Template
POST http://localhost:{PORT}/api/v2/commands
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "name": "Welcome Greeting",
  "command": "/hi1",
  "text": "Hi there, welcome to the channel!"
}

### V2 Commands - Create Another Template
POST http://localhost:{PORT}/api/v2/commands
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

{
  "name": "Hello Template",
  "command": "/hi2",
  "text": "Hello and welcome to the server"
}

### V2 Search - Command Search (Prioritized)
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/api/v2/commands/search?q=/hi&limit=8
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

### V2 Search - Keyword Search
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/api/v2/commands/search?q=welcome&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

### V2 Search - Edge Case: Just Slash
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/api/v2/commands/search?q=/&limit=8
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

### V2 Search - No Results
GET http://localhost:{PORT}/api/v2/commands/search?q=nonexistent&limit=8
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN_HERE>

